c: 12
v: 36
t: Nuko (Yusufu) yinjirana n’abasore babiri muri gereza. Umwe muri bo aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri narose nenga inzoga.” Undi aravuga ati “Mu by’ukuri njye narose nikoreye imigati ku mutwe inyoni ziyindiraho.” (Baravuga bati) “Dusobanurire iby’izo nzozi. Mu by’ukuri tubona uri mu bakora ibyiza.”